    {
      "type": "section",
      "title": "👯 Correlative Conjunctions (जोड़ी संयोजक)",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "ये संयोजक <b>जोड़े में</b> प्रयोग होते हैं और वाक्य के दो भागों को <b>संतुलित</b> करते हैं।"
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "content": {
            "title": "👥 Correlative Pairs",
            "headers": ["Pair", "अर्थ", "Example", "हिंदी"],
            "rows": [
              ["<b>Both...and</b>", "दोनों...और", "<b>Both</b> Ram <b>and</b> Shyam came.", "<b>दोनों</b> राम <b>और</b> श्याम आए।"],
              ["<b>Either...or</b>", "या तो...या", "<b>Either</b> tea <b>or</b> coffee.", "<b>या तो</b> चाय <b>या</b> कॉफ़ी।"],
              ["<b>Neither...nor</b>", "न...न", "<b>Neither</b> he <b>nor</b> I know.", "<b>न</b> वह जानता है <b>न</b> मैं।"],
              ["<b>Not only...but also</b>", "न केवल...बल्कि", "He is <b>not only</b> smart <b>but also</b> kind.", "वह <b>न केवल</b> होशियार है, <b>बल्कि</b> दयालु भी है।"],
              ["<b>Whether...or</b>", "चाहे...या", "<b>Whether</b> you come <b>or</b> not, I'll go.", "<b>चाहे</b> तुम आओ <b>या</b> न आओ, मैं जाऊँगा।"],
              ["<b>No sooner...than</b>", "जैसे ही...वैसे ही", "<b>No sooner</b> did I reach <b>than</b> it rained.", "<b>जैसे ही</b> मैं पहुँचा <b>वैसे ही</b> बारिश हुई।"],
              ["<b>Hardly/Scarcely...when</b>", "मुश्किल से...तभी", "<b>Hardly</b> had I slept <b>when</b> phone rang.", "<b>मुश्किल से</b> मैं सोया <b>तभी</b> फोन बजा।"],
              ["<b>The more...the more</b>", "जितना ज्यादा...उतना ज्यादा", "<b>The more</b> you read, <b>the more</b> you learn.", "<b>जितना ज्यादा</b> पढ़ो, <b>उतना ज्यादा</b> सीखो।"]
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "note",
          "content": "<b>Subject-Verb Agreement:</b><br>• <b>Both...and</b> = Plural verb (Both Ram <b>and</b> Shyam <b>are</b> here.)<br>• <b>Either...or / Neither...nor</b> = Verb agrees with <b>nearest subject</b> (Neither he <b>nor</b> I <b>am</b> wrong.)"
        }
      ]
    },
