    {
      "type": "section",
      "title": "❌ Common Mistakes (सामान्य गलतियाँ)",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "table",
          "content": {
            "title": "🚫 इन गलतियों से बचें",
            "headers": ["❌ गलत", "✅ सही", "Explanation"],
            "rows": [
              ["<b>Although</b> he is poor, <b>but</b> he is honest.", "<b>Although</b> he is poor, he is honest.", "Although/Though के साथ But नहीं लगाएं।"],
              ["<b>Because</b> of he was ill, he didn't come.", "<b>Because</b> he was ill, he didn't come.", "Because of + Noun; Because + Clause."],
              ["<b>Unless</b> you don't study, you will fail.", "<b>Unless</b> you study, you will fail.", "Unless = If not (पहले से negative)."],
              ["I will wait <b>unless</b> you come.", "I will wait <b>until</b> you come.", "Until = Time; Unless = Condition."],
              ["He is <b>both</b> smart <b>as well as</b> kind.", "He is <b>both</b> smart <b>and</b> kind.", "Both...and = सही जोड़ी।"],
              ["<b>No sooner</b> I reached <b>when</b> it rained.", "<b>No sooner</b> did I reach <b>than</b> it rained.", "No sooner...than (with inversion)."],
              ["<b>Hardly</b> I slept <b>than</b> phone rang.", "<b>Hardly</b> had I slept <b>when</b> phone rang.", "Hardly/Scarcely...when."]
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "note",
          "content": "<b>याद रखें:</b><br>• <b>Although/Though/Even though</b> + <b>But</b> = ❌<br>• <b>Unless</b> + <b>Not</b> = ❌<br>• <b>No sooner...than</b> (not when)<br>• <b>Hardly/Scarcely...when</b> (not than)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "title": "📝 Summary (सारांश)",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "list",
          "content": [
            "<b>Coordinating (FANBOYS):</b> For, And, Nor, But, Or, Yet, So - समान भाग जोड़ते हैं।",
            "<b>Subordinating:</b> Because, If, When, While, Although, Unless - Main + Subordinate clause.",
            "<b>Correlative:</b> Both...and, Either...or, Neither...nor, Not only...but also - जोड़े में।",
            "<b>Conjunctive Adverbs:</b> However, Therefore, Moreover - Semicolon के साथ।",
            "<b>Confusing:</b> When (point) vs While (duration), Until (time) vs Unless (condition).",
            "<b>Mistakes:</b> Although + but ❌, Unless + not ❌, No sooner...when ❌."
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
